{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd154e214c","title":"前言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5e7f0cb461","index":0,"year":1976,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"bd154e214c"}],"tags":[{"id":"0422885d2e","name":"中共上海电影制片厂委员会","type":"出版方/发行方"},{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"8e2c446eb1","name":"王洪文","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","name":"揭发“四人帮”王洪文插手控制上影阴谋篡党夺权的罪行（1976.12）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"王洪文、马天水、徐景贤、黄涛，1976.12，反攻倒算材料，中共上海电影制片厂委员会","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/1.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/2.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/3.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/4.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/5.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/6.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/7.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/8.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5/9.jpg"}],"authors":[{"id":"24897f83e0","name":"中共上海电影制片厂委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5":{"comments":[{"id":"a020ba2245","publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"中共上海电影制片厂委员会\n一九七六年十二月"}],"contents":[{"id":"5d2835f27b","type":"title","text":"前言","index":0,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"},{"id":"533d586ef9","type":"paragraph","text":"“四人帮”反党集团篡党夺权的野心由来已久，他们早就妄图利用电影等文艺宣传工具为篡党夺权大造反革命舆论。","index":1,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"},{"id":"360f5f050a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们最近召开厂党委对“四人帮”王洪文和马、徐、王直接插手上影等单位，妄图控制电影，作为“四人帮”篡党夺权的一个阵地的有关活动和反革命舆论进行了专题揭发，现将揭发若干材料整理印出来，供全厂同志批判。","index":2,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"},{"id":"436eb2a9d9","type":"paragraph","text":"这个材料分为三个部分。第一部分是王洪文在一九七五年夏秋背着毛主席、党中央，窜来上海，直接插手上影的罪恶活动和反革命言论。第二部分是王洪文在上海文艺座谈会（即200号会议）上的反革命言论。第三部分是王洪文一九七六年五月在钓鱼台接见张家龙等人的材料。对于每一部分的主要内容和当时的背景我们都加了按语说明。","index":3,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"},{"id":"422c9a86dc","type":"signature","text":"中共上海电影制片厂委员会","index":4,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"},{"id":"24c1fa90dc","type":"signature","text":"一九七六年12月","index":5,"publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c"}],"page":{"id":"80a330f570","publicationId":"8c1a5316-884e-465a-9775-48338f6cc6b5","articleId":"bd154e214c","start":2,"end":2}}}},"__N_SSG":true}